[[File:Cactus Pheasant Classic logo.png|right|100px]] The '''Cactus Pheasant Classic''' was an annual [[curling]] tournament, held in late October in [[Brooks, Alberta]]. It was part of the [[World Curling Tour]]. The purse for the event $70,000 Cdn. It has not been held since 2013.
