Many '''environmental film festivals''' present complete programs of films dedicated to environmental subjects on a regular basis, typically annually. Others are committed to presenting environmental films within their subprograms. The festivals listed below solicit and present films about [[nature]], [[ecology]], [[conservation (ethic)|conservation]], [[wildlife]], [[pollution]], [[habitat loss]], [[climate change]] and related topics. Some of the festivals listed here are also members of the [[Green Film Network]]. This list is not exhaustive.
